This table lists the Battles, Battle Info, Breeder Training, and Invites. The Invites are listed preceding their battle or event. The 109 battles are listed as displayed on the Champion Screen of Breeder info; The in-game list appears to list them as you would get to them within each rank. The A ranked Malkt Cup in Oct. 1 being the only exception. This table is painstakingly exact, down to punctuation. What you see in the game is here. I have made an exact match. The only rhyme or reason I can find to explain the way the battles are listed is as follows:

Rank: E thru S
Month: 1 thru 12
Week: 1 thru 4

Ranks: E thru A
Regular Battles
AGIMA Official Battles
Death Blow Qualifiers #
Death Blow Matches
Amity Cups
Invitation Match Dragon
Invitation Match Durahan

Rank: S
Regular Battles
AGIMA Official Battles
Emperor Cup Qualifiers *
Invitation Match Zan
Emperor Cup
